<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 0c 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />踩在雪上的聲音很悅耳吧？<10_4 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />尤其是踩在剛下的積雪上，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<setNpcTalkChoices chatOption="0" cancelOption="1" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 0c 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗚～<delay20 />我的腿好冷<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay frames="40" />
<colour id="4" />我是不是該穿雙襪子呢<delay8 />…<delay8 />…<setNpcTalkChoices chatOption="0" cancelOption="1" /><colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 0c 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雪能夠讓我沉浸在一種難以言喻的心情當中，<delay8 />
所以我很喜歡雪喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<setNpcTalkChoices chatOption="0" cancelOption="1" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 0c 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="14" />嗨，是你啊！<endTag a="110" b="14" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有沒有<delay20 />享受這場雪呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<setNpcTalkChoices chatOption="0" cancelOption="1" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="06 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在下雪的日子裡，<delay20 />
一些隨處可見且理所當然的事物，<delay8 />
都會變得比平常更美麗呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><setNpcTalkChoices chatOption="0" cancelOption="1" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="15" arg="0x804 0x700 0xcd00" /></message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 0c 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />例如說<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />算了，當我沒說，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<setNpcTalkChoices chatOption="0" cancelOption="1" /></message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="12" arg="0x9 0xa" /></message>
